lemma monotone_construction (hij : i ≤ j) : construction T hT i ⊆ construction T hT j := by
  obtain ⟨k, rfl⟩ := le_iff_exists_add.mp hij;
  apply subset_construction_add;
```

This lemma shows that `construction T hT i ⊆ construction T hT j` if `i ≤ j`. The proof uses `le_iff_exists_add` to write `j = i + k` for some `k`, then applies `subset_construction_add`.

